12/07/2006
ATHENS, Greece -- Preparations for the 15 October local elections are nearing completion, Interior Minister Prokopis Pavlopoulos announced on Tuesday (11 July). 
He was talking to reporters after a cabinet meeting on the issue. 
Pavlopoulos noted that EU member state citizens who reside in Greece would be entitled to vote. 
(Naftemporiki - 12/07/06; ANA-MPA, ERT, Sky Radio - 11/07/06)
